---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About Carlos Jorques, an embedded control systems architect focused on physical systems, automotive software, diagnostics, and technical delivery."
>
	<section class="section">
		<div class="narrow">
			<SectionHeading
				eyebrow="About"
				title="Embedded control systems for physical systems"
				description="I work where software meets the physical world: sensing, signal processing, control logic, diagnostics, actuation, safety expectations, and delivery constraints."
			/>
			<div class="prose">
				<p>
					I am an electrical engineer and PhD-trained control/software engineer focused on
					production-ready embedded control systems. My work connects physical system behavior
					with embedded software architecture, control algorithms, diagnostic strategies, and
					practical implementation constraints.
				</p>
				<p>
					My professional experience includes automotive OEM and Tier 1 environments, where
					engineering quality depends on more than isolated technical decisions. Requirements,
					interfaces, supplier collaboration, safety-related development, A-SPICE expectations,
					AUTOSAR-oriented integration, verification, and delivery timing all shape the solution.
				</p>
				<p>
					My leadership style is technical and alignment-oriented: make the system behavior clear,
					define the responsibilities between disciplines, expose tradeoffs early, and help teams
					move from requirements and concepts toward production software that can be integrated,
					tested, maintained, and trusted.
				</p>
				<p>
					I am especially interested in physical systems, embedded control architecture,
					diagnostics, and reliable machine behavior - the engineering layer that helps smart
					machines sense, decide, protect themselves, and act.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container about-grid">
			<div class="panel about-card">
				<p class="eyebrow">Profile</p>
				<h2>Technical depth with delivery context</h2>
				<p>
					PhD-trained electrical engineer with experience across embedded control, diagnostics,
					safety-related development, software/control integration, and cross-functional delivery.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="panel about-card">
				<p class="eyebrow">Operating mode</p>
				<h2>Architecture, alignment, implementation</h2>
				<p>
					I help connect stakeholders and engineering disciplines around clear system behavior,
					realistic interfaces, and production-ready embedded control decisions.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<ContactCTA />
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 18px;
	}

	.about-card {
		display: grid;
		gap: 14px;
		padding: 28px;
	}

	.about-card h2 {
		font-size: 2.05rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.about-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.about-card h2 {
			font-size: 1.65rem;
		}
	}
</style>
